Thesis:
€10M early-stage fund in Poland to invest in diverse teams building epic businesses. Diverse teams are those founded by at least one woman co-founder or
immigrant representative.

We target 80% of our pipeline being diverse teams based in Poland;
The rest represents the Polish, Belarusian and Ukrainian diaspora all around the world (preliminary in the USA and UK);
We invest with the average ticket size of €200K for pre-seed investments, and €300K for seed investments with the potential of follow-on investments;
We are sector agnostic, but looking for strong founder-market fit and believe in founders building software-first products with high growth potential;
For pre-seed investments we are considering pre-revenue startups, but MVP-ready, for seed investments with first recurring revenue traction.
